name: SofaCat
description: SofaCat is a fun and engaging memecoin project that brings humor and creativity to the crypto space. At its core, SofaCat revolves around the idea that every cat loves a cozy sofa - only to destroy it! This playful narrative brings the community together in a lighthearted way. With SofaCat, you can take part in the fun by helping the cat wreck sofas on our interactive website, all while engaging with a growing, enthusiastic community. It’s more than just a meme - it’s a shared experience of fun and excitement!
